text: Roosdaal is a municipality in the Belgian province of Flemish Brabant. In 2007, 10788 people lived there. It is at 50° 50 North, 04° 04 East. == Famous people == * Frans Van Cauwelaert (10 January 1880 – 17 May 1961), politician and lawyer. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities of Flemish Brabant
